title: Zeeek Run v1.0.2
description:
The world of sound and harmonics is in great danger! Silencio and his hordes of Sighs Silences and decided to cut the music and sounds to none.

Take control of Zeeek, the last hope against the threat of Silences, browse many different levels to the humor and fight more powerful enemies!

Discover this brand new exclusive runner musical pace resulting in the colors go wild and enjoy your journey through the different world!

Prepare to conquer the terrible Silencio and his cronies, unleash the rock star in you and catch sequences of musical notes to become "Super Zeeek" the invincible global scores and blow!

Who will be the best rocker in the world?

Features:

High definition graphics
30 different levels
4 worlds to discover
Cloud Save (Sync save between your smartphone and tablet !)
Incredible music!
An expert mode for the more adventurous!

What's New:

Update 1.0.2
- New animations
- Speed Expert difficulty
- Many bug fixes!
